---
title: Peri Peri Spiced Chorizo Pilaf with Peas and Soured Cream
description: This Peri Peri Spiced Chorizo Pilaf combines the Indian technique of pilaf, a sautéed rice dish, with Portuguese flavours. Peri peri contains smoked paprika, ancho chilli powder, ground cumin and oregano.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R38_W41_UK_F19947-4_Main_low_2-cb3dae85.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/66b22e2f6e2625457a71ce96-en-GB.pdf
cuisine: Portuguese
nutrition:
  calories: 796 kcal
  fat: 37.9 g
  saturated fat: 18.6 g
  carbohydrates: 96.6 g
  sugar: 20.5 g
  protein: 25.4 g
  fiber: 9.4 g
  sodium: 5 g
  serving size: 549
time required: 45 minutes
author: Anushka Magan
